</para></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><emphasis role="bold">Example:</emphasis></term>
<listitem><para>The following example initializes tree view 101 by sending message ADD
to object &quot;tc&quot;, which is assigned to 101 by using GetTreeControl:
<programlisting>
<![CDATA[
::class MyDlgClass subclass UserDialog inherit AdvancedControls

::method InitDialog
  tc = self~GetTreeControl(101)
  if tc == .Nil then return
  tc~Add("Root 1")
  tc~Add(  ,"Item 1")
  tc~Add(  ,"Item 2")
  tc~Add(  ,"Item 3")
  tc~Add("Root 2", , ,"EXPANDED")
  tc~Add(  ,"Item 4", , ,"BOLD")
  tc~Add(  ,"Item 5")
  tc~Add(  ,"Subroot")
  tc~Add(  ,    ,"Item 6",3)
]]>
</programlisting>
</para></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist>

